•   the implementation of DWS’s strategic initiatives and other responses there to;
•   the development of aspects of DWS’s results of operations;
•   DWS’s expectations of the impact of risks that affect its business, including the risks
    of losses on DWS’s trading processes and credit exposures;
•   the progress and timing of transfers to form the Group and related staff and resource
    transfers from DB Group; and
•   other statements relating to DWS’s future business development and economic
    performance.

